Name: Moze
Desc: A Shadow Guard of the Yaoqing, Moze is taciturn and solitary, always acting on his own.\nAs an expert in intelligence services and other operations that must remain covert, Moze rarely shows himself before others. The moment he reveals his blade usually spells doom for his enemies.\nHe commands a vast wealth of assassination techniques, coupled with an extraordinary obsession for orderliness and cleanliness.

1.Name: Oathkeeper
1.Desc: After entering battle, Moze regenerates <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> Energy. Each time the Additional DMG from his Talent is triggered, Moze regenerates <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Energy.

2.Name: Wrathbearer
2.Desc: When all allies deal DMG to the enemy target marked as "Prey," increases CRIT DMG by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.

3.Name: Deathchaser
3.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

4.Name: Heathprowler
4.Desc: When using Ultimate, increases the DMG dealt by Moze by <unbreak>#1[f1]%</unbreak>, lasting for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

5.Name: Truthbender
5.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

6.Name: Faithbinder
6.Desc: Increases the DMG multiplier of the Talent's follow-up attack by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.

122301.Name: Hurlthorn
122301.Desc: Deals Lightning DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Moze's ATK to a single target enemy.

122302.Name: Fleetwinged Raid
122302.Desc: Marks a designated single enemy target as "Prey" and deals to it Lightning DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Moze's ATK, and gains <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> points of Charge.\nWhen there are no other characters on the field that are capable of combat, Moze cannot use his Skill and dispels the enemy's "Prey" state.

122303.Name: <unbreak>Dash In,</unbreak> <unbreak>Gash Out</unbreak>
122303.Desc: Deals Lightning DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Moze's ATK to a single target enemy, and launches the Talent's <u>follow-up attack</u> against this target. If the target is defeated before this <u>follow-up attack</u> is used, then launches the <u>follow-up attack</u> against a random single enemy instead.

122304.Name: Cascading Featherblade
122304.Desc: When "Prey" exists on the field, Moze will enter the <u>Departed</u> state.\nAfter allies attack "Prey," Moze will additionally deal 1 instance of Lightning <u>Additional DMG</u> equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of his ATK and consumes 1 point of Charge. For every <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> point(s) of Charge consumed, Moze launches 1 <u>follow-up attack</u> to "Prey," dealing Lightning DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak></color> of his ATK. When Charge reaches 0, dispels the target's "Prey" state and resets the tally of Charge points required to launch <u>follow-up attack</u>. Talent's <u>follow-up attack</u> does not consume Charge.

122306.Name: Attack
122306.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

122307.Name: Bated Wings
122307.Desc: After using Technique, enters the Stealth state for <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> second(s). While in Stealth, Moze is undetectable by enemies. If Moze attacks enemies to enter combat while in Stealth, increases DMG by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>, lasting for <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

1.PointDesc: After using the Talent's follow-up attack, recovers <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Skill Point(s). This effect can trigger again after <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).
When Moze dispels his Departed state, his action advances by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. At the start of each wave, Moze's action advances by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.
When dealing DMG by using Ultimate, it is considered as having launched a follow-up attack. The follow-up attack DMG taken by "Prey" increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.
